{"tid":139453,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，我又整左個「海膽紫薯芝士抹茶杯麵」","createTime":"2017-03-01T12:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T05:01:02.000Z","uid":68594,"like":192,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02c89e784c580af117373510c5bc68c3e39e0f8a","tid":139453,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"話說前排大熱嘅抹茶杯面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/899L53A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F899L53A.jpg&h=645ef938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我食完真心好失望，一啲抹茶味都冇，仲要冇我最心愛嘅紫薯海膽同埋芝士！真係離哂大譜！為咗展示乜嘢先係真正嘅抹茶杯麵，我決定展示真正嘅食譜俾大家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食材今次簡單啲，因為我無錢啦！今次就改用完全759系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oc55776.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOc55776.jpg&h=a7c089a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海膽米餅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yF8G0c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyF8G0c7.jpg&h=63ac9f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡樂B紫薯脆條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6A92O9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6A92O9.jpg&h=21dac82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n合味道大杯面-海鮮味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/of0E5z0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fof0E5z0.jpg&h=fc4d5a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伊藤園抹茶-濃！（一定要濃！）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E37d43x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE37d43x.jpg&h=a3bac2e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡夫芝士片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7W81Am4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7W81Am4.jpg&h=c94ee849&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c6a4817404d84a32784f6e6aa7b9b9fa1937f44","tid":139453,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:21:10.000Z","msg":"食杯麵第一件事梗係要煲水啦！由於今次我哋改用抹茶既關係！我哋梗係要用廚房嘅神器之一，微波爐來叮熱佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vcr69TU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVcr69TU.jpg&h=977e587d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C45zU35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC45zU35.jpg&h=ba0d462a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3分鐘就夠架啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d92066d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd92066d.jpg&h=fc3c55cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱到水蒸氣都升埋上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0nJ5a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0nJ5a2.jpg&h=7aa0af3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後梗係倒落個杯麵度啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/196t2ix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F196t2ix.jpg&h=b517ab97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係依個時候就要即刻加塊芝士片落去!!睇落幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYCVQxT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYCVQxT.jpg&h=b2766366&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65b5a1134db50d22a15d1e3a7325435632a11405","tid":139453,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72084c68aa15daeac1719c494ebd88f0f15f1265","tid":139453,"uid":9382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1181c2036f6b11d647f5a63684dbd851b13f60","tid":139453,"uid":83709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:23:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78f9e06fc3bf4e667f55539dfbc4ab0c1f16ef94","tid":139453,"uid":72974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"嘔緊未"},{"pid":"a9d9a6cae7225d9ccbfef6a27fab549957b642f7","tid":139453,"uid":23235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:24:35.000Z","msg":"F5"},{"pid":"71eb8476c0c138887ab02405bc0d4ccfddfb6a22","tid":139453,"uid":76131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"你呢兜野連閻羅王都話極邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a19a1abaebccc80f3cc3853d107f7370cb127d","tid":139453,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:25:46.000Z","msg":"快啦屌你"},{"pid":"31544dfe4b3212581dc871524120c2cd194c5cfa","tid":139453,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:26:42.000Z","msg":"唔影隻手都好地地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00343b00d78825557847ea529b322c812d967f25","tid":139453,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"塊卡夫邊度變出黎"},{"pid":"2b4ad4012e84e4c0b7dfe43d0a49c56cae491cef","tid":139453,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25445a7ae6b105c34646548ff09386b9b4c71c33","tid":139453,"uid":23405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:30:04.000Z","msg":"欣賞你份人夠認真，留名"},{"pid":"d696a8dda27e6672cc4817bb51c30f12b818098b","tid":139453,"uid":68594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"之後專心打個飛機，等佢3分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYCVQxT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYCVQxT.jpg&h=b2766366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一打開蓋，哇！屌！啲芝士已經溶晒落個麵度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4F52Cb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4F52Cb5.jpg&h=cc15ca50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住就落埋個海膽米餅落去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ai1h95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ai1h95.jpg&h=e1b5ea53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同啲紫薯脆條，我想講呢紫薯脆條真係好難食，本身已經好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18XUm96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18XUm96.jpg&h=e8aad17f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCDr1ME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCDr1ME.jpg&h=b347c534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講下味道先，食落去好重奶味，可能係因為啲芝士嘅關係，食落去都偏鹹，其次今次麵吸收左抹茶嘅精華，食落有少少苦澀嘅味道，再配上米餅同脆條，浸濕左嘅米餅吸哂咁湯，食到後尾快重融化左係個湯入邊，啲紫薯就唔講，真係好撚難食，總結嚟講，我係唔會浪費食物嘅，完<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2zQ6qP8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zQ6qP8.jpg&h=c55d5e47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58244e8e208f9af2c0d3a10804d2c6a68642deee","tid":139453,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:31:22.000Z","msg":"好邪惡呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1ee5851b0288fb6d76f34a1057bd3f2a28aac4","tid":139453,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9824b2b5304302777787557481e846